⚠️ Data Usage Restriction

The dataset(s) included in this repository (under the `/data/` folder or otherwise) are part of **ongoing, unpublished academic research**.

They are provided **strictly for demonstration and code review purposes only**.

By accessing or downloading this data, you agree to the following:

- You **may not** use the data in any research publication, presentation, or report.
- You **may not** copy, redistribute, republish, or rehost the data in any form.
- You **may not** create derivative works or train new models using this data.
- You **may view** and inspect the data solely for understanding the accompanying code.

Manual copying, scraping, or distribution of the data files is strictly **prohibited**.  
**Legal action may be taken** in case of any violation of these terms.

If you are interested in using the data for collaboration or review, please contact the author: **Arkajeet Bhattacharjee**.
